pull.title: Install bitcoin-wallet manpage
pull.body: This change marks the already-existing `bitcoin-wallet.1` manpage file for installation together with the others.  Previously, only `bitcoind.1`, `bitcoin-cli.1`, `bitcoin-tx.1` and `bitcoin-qt.1` would be installed.

events.message:
Install bitcoin-wallet manpage.

This change marks the already-existing bitcoin-wallet.1 manpage file for
installation together with the others.  Previously, only bitcoind.1,
bitcoin-cli.1, bitcoin-tx.1 and bitcoin-qt.1 would be installed.
